{"tid":1228832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90後同00後可能會係最後一代既香港人","createTime":"2019-06-15T18:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T05:49:27.000Z","uid":19445,"like":131,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4072cb419213efad3ef9ac54eebb80a55ba0f7","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"今日係街行過聽到小學雞傾計，竟然係全程用普通話溝通 <br />\n冇.撚.錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係一句廣東話都冇講過<br />\n我唔知佢地識唔識廣東話<br />\n但眼見依家越黎越多支那人落黎 <br />\n用佢地既語言同文化 赤化香港 <br />\n我覺得好灰心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我曾經以為未來係我地有希望同港共政權 鬥長命 我地贏唔到 我地既下一代同你鬥到底<br />\n上一代唔支持 話我地搞事唔緊要 <br />\n我地可以教育下一代 <br />\n以為將來會越來越多覺得自己係香港人既下一代出黎抗爭 <br />\n但到頭來呢班10後連廣東話都唔識<br />\n而佢既支那老母一定教佢係中國人，香港等於支那<br />\n更加唔好期望佢會覺得中國同香港有分別<br />\n細個玩抖音講大陸潮語，都期望入到中學可以醒覺 <br />\n思想可以透過媒體同教育改變 <br />\n但母語改變唔到 細個唔講廣東話 唔通到中學先開始學咩<br />\n更恐怖既人呢班人人數絕對唔少 甚至已經係主流既地位 完全冇講廣東話既必要<br />\n（有錯既話希望更正，話比我知事實唔係咁）<br />\n好希望做老師既 或者為人父母既 <br />\n一定要教細路講廣東話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔知過多廿年我地會唔會成為最後一代覺得自己係香港人既人 <br />\n但係 希望我地盡我地既能力 <br />\n就算點都好 大家愛呢個地方既 <br />\n都盡力 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">保衛香港 <br />\n聽日 維園見 </span>"},{"pid":"d9481c1e70c74f981364e0d662c0ab9e181b5152","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1120586354811676&amp;id=153300521509664&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1120586354811676%26id%3D153300521509664%26refsrc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F%26_rdr&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=b764c4a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1120586354811676&amp;id=153300521509664&amp;refsrc=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"12802dfed1e24bd328fc59dc41740e9672b09463","tid":1228832,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:22:56.000Z","msg":"係, 我都經常見到"},{"pid":"39f8267394c6d603cfece62359cbfb7eb0982c56","tid":1228832,"uid":256639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:24:07.000Z","msg":"幾歲果d喺街見到都係講支話"},{"pid":"39ce7f7afb2fe12e7fd0c510c22e1ed8974d6dc9","tid":1228832,"uid":15205,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"咪再分咩年代出世 , 下一代唔醒覺就教到佢醒覺"},{"pid":"5a1fd008310c7e532266d22dafe07fc4b4f51835","tid":1228832,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"[金鐘宣言] 希望聽日能夠朗讀出金鐘宣言俾全世界人民聽到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1228072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1228072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c828fa7da14ec08db5dd8c624cd821ab447df720","tid":1228832,"uid":258927,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/589475668207599620/589520404989607965/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F589520404989607965%2Funknown.png&h=d689c460&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ffdb19a25bca0c114a2812da70805f8e7332926","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:25:53.000Z","msg":"唔知點做先可以改變呢個局面<br />\n語言一定係要長時間教先識<br />\n唔肯講既話基本上點教都冇用"},{"pid":"23f12f4775c4646bbaa828d35bc3fbcc489f72f9","tid":1228832,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最終目標：完全撤回送中惡法。釋放義士。<br />\n<br />\n暫你老母緩呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗我地仲未打贏就已經有巴打以死相諫，唔好掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行。  星期一出去集會。<br />\n<br />\n你仲可以唔出黎？<br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fcb007a911383098bcfc2adde0112a2f92d42c5","tid":1228832,"uid":245126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:26:41.000Z","msg":"中學雞都好多講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去一轉深圳關口有大量往返深圳香港返學既學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c024c27321886c6614b8ab8b4227c32518971236","tid":1228832,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:28:52.000Z","msg":"唔怕，其實係一部份黎嫁炸<br />\n<br />\n80後都講過，見90後個個都識寫簡體字，覺得90後已經係中國人<br />\n<br />\n90後又覺得00後玩抖音飲喜茶係中國人<br />\n<br />\n其實骨子裡都係香港人多，只係個環境，表面上有d野真係要做。"},{"pid":"3c20f12c3d0cea02ee5e19cad5c5fefed9fb1e94","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39ce7f7afb2fe12e7fd0c510c22e1ed8974d6dc9","tid":1228832,"uid":15205,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"咪再分咩年代出世 , 下一代唔醒覺就教到佢醒覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"屌就緊係要屌 <br />\n但如果條友連廣東話都唔識 <br />\n其實根本佢都唔覺得香港同中國有分別<br />\n等於要說服一個支那人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138b40b882217d5b18c6fca0425cfcd9a3a1d962","tid":1228832,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:30:47.000Z","msg":"改變班藍絲廢老易啲定班細路易啲？<br />\n連啲老人家我哋都姑且盡力想用長輩圖嚟令佢哋轉軚，何況係班細路<br />\n堅持著，只要捱多兩代，個香港就係我哋o架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a18340a1c25b020c78b12df80ac70b153a65f93","tid":1228832,"uid":207462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"重點係思想要教到佢地似個香港人<br />\n6&middot;9其實都有新移民醒覺 同土生土長香港人一齊反送中<br />\n只欠在大部分新移民俾中共洗腦洗得太勁<br />\n落到嚟又俾建制派洗多次腦<br />\n只要有心 要將佢地變番正常唔係冇可能<br />\n重點係 語言只係嘅溝通媒介 我地要改變嘅 係佢地嗰套俾中共灌輸嘅思想"},{"pid":"162c7c5b8466ea81cd6711b49c96b236e766bad0","tid":1228832,"uid":195462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"點止小學<br />\n前幾日食m記 一台3個中學女仔<br />\n都係全程各睇手機 普通話溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca2c7d166e39ce54d83bb1faf869e315df87fd","tid":1228832,"uid":50987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:32:53.000Z","msg":"要比信心下一代，當初00後咪又係俾人笑"},{"pid":"67d30794471fab170b327020830f8edf6f18eff8","tid":1228832,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fc22781d4fbda1973cbceb473d3b8d8989ebf8","tid":1228832,"uid":168267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"六七十年代走佬落嚟嘅<br />\n有潮州佬、上海佬、客家佬，但最後係個個唔多唔少都會變咗講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7199772e6b30850cdbd737ae47af8e87831c3726","tid":1228832,"uid":262079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"逢放學時間見親D小學生都係講普通話<br />\n次次都好有衝動叫佢地收嗲返大陸<br />\n唔敢想象過多十幾年後會變成點..."},{"pid":"1338ffa34c18faf128cdea27508d424f5a54f57d","tid":1228832,"uid":149927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ce7f7afb2fe12e7fd0c510c22e1ed8974d6dc9","tid":1228832,"uid":15205,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"咪再分咩年代出世 , 下一代唔醒覺就教到佢醒覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:11.000Z","msg":"Sor手殘禁錯負評"},{"pid":"c044c0c28873b78fcf555d0e01519a9572a77857","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0fc22781d4fbda1973cbceb473d3b8d8989ebf8","tid":1228832,"uid":168267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"六七十年代走佬落嚟嘅<br />\n有潮州佬、上海佬、客家佬，但最後係個個唔多唔少都會變咗講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"正常去到人地地方 <br />\n就緊係學返人地語言<br />\n最撚慘係一大批蝗一齊落嚟<br />\n令佢地組成到一個大嘅群體 <br />\n唔需要用廣東話都溝通到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71855972c6911fbfa32994b0a28e29e2acc463e4","tid":1228832,"uid":251538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔止小學 我住既附近有間中學<br />\n呢3，4年開始有時間中撞到食飯/放學時間<br />\n聽到全撚部學生都係講普通話<br />\n個種心情真係唔識講 點解香港會變到咁"},{"pid":"7b17a33c5f6f494ed7e12256e5a0338411e3fca5","tid":1228832,"uid":182452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:38:38.000Z","msg":"尋日搭地鐵翻屋企<br />\n有兩個著校服既小學生<br />\n一男一女<br />\n全程用普通話溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7661cc4084b37db74285576f57bf7a3885457c","tid":1228832,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:39:31.000Z","msg":"之前仲好多人大力屌00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未fd番架<br />\n件事過左之後要有人出黎道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03d1bca0490fba4238b1db15083d2640bad2f0f","tid":1228832,"uid":19445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:46:08.000Z","msg":"尤其係呢排<br />\n當我地係度努力緊守護香港既時候<br />\n再聽到班人講蝗語赤化香港<br />\n真係好撚絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}